snippet.title: Nightmare Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
DOWNLOAD NOW! https://nightmare.mageworkstudios.com

Put us on your Steam Wishlist: https://store.steampowered.com/app/1635770/Nightmare/

After six years of continuous development, Magework Studios announces its release of Nightmare - a PvE & PvP balanced MMORPG set in the world of Sylvenus. Join us today!

Official Website: https://nightmare.mageworkstudios.com
